  <tr>
    <td width="50%" valign="top">
		<font color="#9f3215" face="verdana" size="3">
		<strong>Name:</strong><br></font>
		<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
		Bear, Grizzly, Rabid<br><br>
		<font color="#9f3215" face="verdana" size="3">
		<b>Level:</b><br></font>
		<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
		8-10</font><br><br>
		<font color="#9f3215" face="verdana" size="3">
		<b>Aggressive Tendencies:</font></b><br>
		<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
		<u>Attack On Sight</u><br>All Non-Rangers</font><br><br>
		<font color="#9f3215" face="verdana" size="3">
		<b>Loot:</font></b><br>
		<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
		
		<a href="http://www.everlore.com/items/items.asp?mode=show&IID=1429">
		<font face='verdana' size='2' color='black'>Grizzly Bear Skin</a><br>
		
		
		
		<a href="http://www.everlore.com/items/items.asp?mode=show&IID=1427">
		<font face='verdana' size='2' color='#2C4161'>Low Quality Bear Pelt</a><br>
		
		
		
		<a href="http://www.everlore.com/items/items.asp?mode=show&IID=1505">
		<font face='verdana' size='2' color='black'>Putrid Bear Hide</a><br>
		
		
		
		<a href="http://www.everlore.com/items/items.asp?mode=show&IID=1426">
		<font face='verdana' size='2' color='#2C4161'>Ruined Bear Pelt</a><br>
		
		
		
		</font>		
		<p>
		<font color="#9f3215" face="verdana" size="3">
		<b>Special Abilities:</b><br>
		<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
		Disease</font></td>
 
 
 
 
 
   
	<td width="50%" valign="top">
		<font color="#9f3215" face="verdana">
		<b>Known Locations:</b>
		</font><br>
		<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
		Qeynos Hills<br>
		
		<br><br>
		<font color="#9f3215" face="verdana" size="3">
		<p><b>Faction Hits:</b></font>
		<font color="#9f3215" face="verdana" size="2">
		<u><b>Worse</b></u><br></font>
		<font face="verdana" size="1" color="black">
		None<br>
		<br>
		<font color="#9f3215" face="verdana" size="2">
		<u><b>Better</b></u><br></font><font face="verdana" size="1" color="black">
		None<br>
		<br>
		</p></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan="3" width="100%"><p align="center">
    <font color="#9f3215" face="verdana" size="2">These are just a little weaker than a regular grizzly, and worth a little less in exp too.  They are really not worth chasing after to kill, and the risks are too great unless you are completing the quest for diseased pelts.  These animals are protected by the rangers of Qeynos Hills and they give diseased pelts which are pretty much useless for tailoring.  They not only hit hard, but give you rabies, which takes 10-20 minutes to go away without a cleric.</font></td>
  </tr>
